<div id="review_3489106743" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/3489106743" />
    <a title="Gregory Knapp" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/48482416-gregory-knapp"><img alt="Gregory Knapp" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1446412563p2/48482416.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/3489106743?book_show_action=true">Nov 20, 2020</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Gregory Knapp" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Gregory Knapp" href="/user/show/48482416-gregory-knapp">Gregory Knapp</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

          <div class="uitext greyText bookshelves">
            Shelves:
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=american-history">american-history</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=non-fiction">non-fiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=to-read-own">to-read-own</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=nonfiction">nonfiction</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=lincoln">lincoln</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=civil-war">civil-war</a>, 
              <a class="actionLinkLite" href="/review/list/48482416-gregory-knapp?shelf=history">history</a>
          </div>
    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer3489106743" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer8749786475439827839">This was an interesting book but a little dry. There are long sections about his methodology, followed by stories based on periods of the war, followed by summary or conclusions. Not a bad approach but it was choppy. From a large number of his conclusions/summaries, it was clear to me that McPherson was writing from a strongly Yankee perspective, as opposed to a neutral, data driven approach, which was his premise he stated in the beginning of the book. That put me off quite a bit. </span>

          </span>
        </div>


