<div id="review_2058390241" class="review" itemprop="reviews" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Review">
  <link itemprop="url" href="https://www.goodreads.com/review/show/2058390241" />
    <a title="Cameron" class="left imgcol" href="/user/show/5322582-cameron"><img alt="Cameron" src="https://images.gr-assets.com/users/1355886896p2/5322582.jpg" /></a>

  <div class="left bodycol">
    <div class="reviewHeader uitext stacked">
        <a class="reviewDate createdAt right" href="/review/show/2058390241?book_show_action=true">Nov 06, 2017</a>

      <span itemprop="author" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Person">
        <a title="Cameron" class="user" itemprop="url" name="Cameron" href="/user/show/5322582-cameron">Cameron</a>
      </span>

        rated it
        <span class=" staticStars notranslate" title="really liked it"><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10">really liked it</span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p10"></span><span size="15x15" class="staticStar p0"></span></span>



        

    </div>


        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer2058390241" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer18316703272320443100">It&apos;s a little dry reading a bunch of excerpts of letters, but it&apos;s worth it to really understand the soldiers&apos; motivations. The war was about slavery and union. Soldiers were remarkably aware of politics and had daily discussions in camp. </span>
  <span id="freeText18316703272320443100" style="display:none">It's a little dry reading a bunch of excerpts of letters, but it's worth it to really understand the soldiers' motivations. The war was about slavery and union. Soldiers were remarkably aware of politics and had daily discussions in camp. </span>
  <a data-text-id="18316703272320443100" href="#" onclick="swapContent($(this));; return false;">...more</a>

          </span>
        </div>


